README.md


// Why I Built This

I'm currently learning Data Engineering and wanted a project that goes beyond tutorials.
This project gave me hands-on experience working with APIs, JSON data, data transformation, and exploratory analysis. It also helped me understand how data moves from a source system into a format that can be used for reporting and insights.

// Next Steps

A few things I'd like to add in future versions:

* Historical trend tracking
* DuckDB for analytics
* Automated data collection
* Interactive dashboards
* Language growth comparisons over time

This project is part of my journey into Data Engineering and building practical experience with ETL pipelines.
